"129.8.242.109","CVE-2013-1635","80","tcp","Apache httpd","2.2.15",,"7.5","7.5","2.0","ext/soap/soap.c in PHP before 5.3.22 and 5.4.x before 5.4.13 does not validate the relationship between the soap.wsdl_cache_dir directive and the open_basedir directive, which allows remote attackers to bypass intended access restrictions by triggering the creation of cached SOAP WSDL files in an arbitrary directory.","0.03157","0.87246","false","false","California State University at Fresno","California State University at Fresno","AS2037","ipeer.ts.fresnostate.edu,ipeer.ad.csufresno.edu","fresnostate.edu,csufresno.edu",,"US","Fresno","2026-06-16T18:41:56.040453"
